        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2022-05-20 07:49:02.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> Patch Set 3:\n> \n> These values will have to change every time we do a release. If so, we should automate this.\n\nAgree. Do we already have the automate method to do this? Because there are so many versions in a bunch of pom.xml files need to be changed in Policy during the release process, so I guess there may already have schema to do this automatically.",
